Read the Spreadsheet: Use a library like pandas to read the spreadsheet and extract the birthdays along with the corresponding names.

Calculate Reminders: Calculate how many days are left until each birthday. You can use the datetime module to work with dates.

Send WhatsApp Messages: You can use the twilio library to send messages via WhatsApp. You'll need to sign up for a Twilio account and get your Twilio credentials.


